descriptionNullable:
One Piece is an anime series adapted from the manga by Eiichiro Oda. The story follows as the main character Luffy, a 17-year old rubber boy, sets out on an adventure in the sea to find the One Piece and become the King of Pirates while having his own pirate crew called 'Strawhat Pirates'. 

The data was collected from IMDB and Wikipedia. 

I recently started learning python :) This is the second dataset I have created. Looking forward to exploring more about python.
